data.name: lblRules.Text
data.value: Rules: Once the game starts you will have the option to enter more words if you like. Each word must be between 4 - 8 letters long and contain at least 2 vowels. The current words are all nature related. Once the game starts you will try and guess the random word that the game has chosen. You will have 5 attempts to guess that correct word and if you're stuck hints will be provided. Enjoy!!

data.name: lblRead.Text
data.value: PLEASE READ: When you first hit play, to continue you must hit either the yes or no button where it asks you if you want to enter more words to continue!! All pre-selected words start with a capital letter!
